description:
Trump Inauguration, Making America Great Again, and Bible Prophecy - On January 20, 2017, White Horse Media streamed LIVE through our Youtube Channel the Donald J. Trump Presidential Inauguration ceremony. Pastor Wohlberg introduced this special event to participants, then we switched to the live feed of the Inauguration. Following the ceremony, Pastor Steve Wohlberg made comments and fielded questions for about an hour. Our focus was on God’s prophecy of Revelation 13:11-16, the role of the United States of America in end-time events, the significance of the U.S. constitution, and our personal preparation for the soon return of Jesus Christ (see Revelation 14:14-16). Discover what NBC, ABC, Fox News and CNN won’t tell you. Please share widely on Social Media. Watch the replay now!
